      "title": "The official announcement of the President's resignation this morning",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Sources in the Speaker's office say that the official announcement regarding the resignation of President Gotabaya Rajapaksa from his office will be issued by Speaker Mahinda Yapa Abeywardena this morning.",
        "The President's letter of resignation was received by the speaker last night and the announcement will be issued after checking the legal situation."
      ],
